Product name: Tin toy English banker's box
Description:
I found this pixie-sized metal box in Philadelphia.  It's an adorable toy version of an English Banker's box or document box; complete with the same signature paint colors and striping.  There is some obvious paint loss, but the gold paint is especially vibrant even after all these years.
The box measures just 3 inches long, 2 inches wide and is 1.5 inches tall (with lid on) and 1 inch deep.  The latch is most definitely challenged.  It doesn't want to remain closed, but it does look like with the proper skeleton key, the mechanism would work.
The carrying handle is intact and moves nicely.  There is rust on the bottom of the piece and the paint loss I already mentioned.  It is marked "English Make" on the back.
It's a lovely collectible and would look sweet in a vignette.  It's definiely a unique, hard to find piece.
Note **** the doll is simply a display piece and NOT included with the box.

Product name: Maxaloones, Maxaloone pants, You are my Sunshine cloth diaper pants, grow with me pants, monsterbunz, baby leggings, leggings, babywearing
Description:
You are my Sunshine Maxaloones! 
This listing is for one pair of Maxaloones in your choice of size!
Maxaloones are seriously fun pants made in a "grow with me" style so you get maximum wear in addition to maximum cuteness! The waist band and leg cuffs fold up or down depending on the sizing needs of your kiddo and adjust as he/she grows. They're perfect for babywearing and cloth diapering. The design has extra room in the bum for those cloth diapers and the versitiliy of the legs allows you to keep those tootsies covered while baby wearing by rolling the legs down on chilly nights! 
This listing features a You are my Sunshine print in soft cotton lycra, with coordinating 
light turquoise leg & waist bands with same bum circle. (bum circle is the backside of the pants, shown in the 1st photo :D ) All seams are completed using a serger and topstitching with a double needle coverstitch.
Sizing - these are a one size fits most and sizing is approximate. 
Squishiloones - Newborn to 3/6 months
Miniloones - 3 months to 12 months
Size 1 - Maxaloones - 6 months to 3 years
Size 2 - Monster Maxaloones - 1 year to 5 years
Silly Sea Turtle is an authorized seamstress and seller of Maxaloones, using an original pattern written by Max and Meena.
All Maxaloones are made in my smoke free and pet free home, with love and attention to detail. All fabrics are prewashed and preshrunk before making them into super cute pants. Most often i use All free and Clear detergent with a snuggle fabric softener sheet in the dryer. Since the fabrics are preshrunk you don't need to worry about them shrinking on you in the wash. In our home i wash our maxaloones on cold, and tumble dry on low. 
These maxaloones are ready to ship and will ship within 48 hours of payment. If your order contains other made to order items, it will ship within approximately 3 weeks (but i always try to be sooner than that) Shipping is a flat rate of 5 regardless of the number of items you buy! Is your order going to be 75 or more? Use coupon code SHIPITFREE and shipping is on me! 
(for my international friends, spend 75 or more and receive a 5 discount on your order. WORLDWIDEFRIEND. And if you are overcharged on shipping, i will always refund the overages! International shipping is also flat rate regardless of the number of items you buy! )
Please contact me with any questions - i am happy to work with you! 
~amy

Description:
Matching Pair of Retro Industrial Vinyl Swivel Chairs - Up to set of 8 chairs
Lovely opportunity to own a stunning pair of original 70s Industiral swivel chairs. These are an original item from the 70s and think were used as hairdressers or barbers and are made from a shiny english racing green vinyl with metal base. They have a very nice retro style and egg shape which gives them a funky mid century look. They are not height adjustable but are on swivel metal base which is good comercial type quality.  The chairs are heavy weight and feel to be made very well but ive not seen any chairs like these before or have a brand on the. These chairs would make a strong statement in a retro themed home or bar as they are part of a set of 8.
These pair of chairs come in very good original condition for the age and show minimal wear to the upholstery. The Cushion foam and vinyl still has years in it and will last a long time if looked after. There are no rips, tears or major scuffs to the fabric on any of these chairs. The  chairs have had a light clean and there are no pulls or rips and the quilting part is still in very good condition. 
 
Overall the condition of these chairs are a high 7 out of 10 and although not new they are a very clean example of a well looked after peice of vintage furniture with no signs of heavy use.
 
I would be happy to sell separate but there are 8 of these chairs avalible and happy to do a discount to take all the chairs.

Product name: Ticking Stripe Dog Bed Cover, Custom Pet Bed Cover, Dog Bed Duvet Cover, Modern Pillow-Style Dog Bed Cover for Small to Large Dog Beds
Description:
This dog bed cover is made from premium upholstery-grade cotton fabric that is beautiful, durable, and machine washable. Stuff it with one of our premium eco-friendly dog bed inserts (sold separately at 
www.etsy.com/listing/489777824),
 an old dog bed, or your own linens or pillows. Each cover is handmade with care in San Francisco.
D E S C R I P T I O N
Our versatile pet bed duvet covers are crafted with an envelope closure on the bottom, which means that there aren't any zippers or buttons for your dog to chew or pull. And, they are sewn using heavy-duty thread and overstitched for durability.
The Ticking Stripe cover features a classic black ticking stripe on a tan background that will complement most homes. The fabric is a heavy-duty 10 oz weight and is one of our most durable covers.
I N S E R T S
This listing is for the cover only.
NEW - we are thrilled to offer premium dog bed inserts stuffed with ecofriendly fiberfill made from recycled plastic bottles, specially formulated to maximize comfort and durability. You can purchase a coordinating insert here: 
www.etsy.com/listing/489777824.
Alternatively, you can easily fill your dog bed cover with pillows (see below for recommendations for each cover size) or old towels, sheets and comforters. This is a great option to easily upcycle old linens, and we've heard that it's especially popular for pets with anxiety issues because they find your scent calming.
S I Z E S
For a perfect fit, we recommend that you measure your pet while it is lying down in its normal sleeping position and then add 10 inches to determine the optimal bed length (the longest dimension). See the size guide in the listing photos for a reference by weight.
XS: 19" x 25". Fits one standard pillow.
S: 20" x 30." Fits one queen size pillow or a size S Foggy Dog insert
M: 25" x 35." Fits two standard pillows or a size M Foggy Dog insert.
L: 30" x 40." Fits two king size pillows or a size L Foggy Dog insert.
XL: 33" x 45". Fits three king size pillows or a size XL Foggy Dog insert.
XXL: 40" x 50". Fits a folded comforter.
Using an existing dog bed inside and need a custom size? We can make almost any size in a rectangular, round, or oval cover. We can also make box-style covers with side panels for memory foam inserts. Just send me a convo and we'll figure out the perfect cover for your needs.
C A R E
Care is easy. Simply machine wash in cold water and tumble dry low.
P E R S O N A L I Z A T I O N
Make your cover extra-special by adding custom embroidery with your dog's name. Available in your choice of fonts and colors. Purchase this listing in addition to the cover: 
www.etsy.com/listing/154105740.
See other sizes, colors and designs in the rest of our shop: 
www.etsy.com/shop/thefoggydog.
Thanks for stopping by!

Product name: Graduation Photo Booth or Party Backdrop
Description:
BACKDROP MATERIALS
All of our backdrops are printed to order on high-quality poly paper or matte vinyl material. 
Our Poly Paper is a synthetic coated paper. It's durable, water-resistant and very difficult to tear. It has a matte finish and a high print quality. Poly Paper does not have a rod pocket and will require clamps for hanging.
Our Vinyl is a high-quality material that is very durable and heavier than Poly Paper. It is water-resistant and can be cleaned easily by wiping away dirt marks with a damp cloth. If properly maintained, this material will last for years. Because of it's durability, Vinyl is the preferred backdrop for cake smashes, floordrops, and pet photography. It has a matte finish and high print quality. Vinyl does not have a rod pocket and will require clamps for hanging. 
BACKDROP SIZES
Our backdrops are available in two size options. All backdrops are listed width x height. Our 4ft wide x 5ft tall backdrops are ideal for newborn photography. Our 5ft wide x 6ft tall backdrops are best for kids and portraits with one or two people. 
EXPEDITED SHIPPING
Every backdrop is printed to order and ships within 1-2 business days via FedEx Ground. We can do expedited shipping by request. Please contact us BEFORE placing your order if you need expedited shipping.
IMPORTANT PRODUCT INFORMATION
Not all computer monitors are calibrated the same. Colors may display differently on your monitor than what is actually printed. We do our best to make sure the image on the product listing is identical to the image you order, however small variations in color can and will occur.

Product name: Deluxe X-Wing Miniatures Template Tray
Description:
By popular demand, I offer you this X-wing miniatures template tray with all of the most popular custom requests all rolled into one.
This is the template tray to hold a full set of maneuver templates for X-Wing Miniatures, including slots for range 1 and range 1-2 templates that are very popular with third party template makers (myself included).  Like all of my template holders, you can press down on the end of a template to easily pop it up out of the tray for use.
The deluxe tray is made of high quality baltic birch wood and has a piece of black felt on the back to protect the templates, keep them from ever sliding out through the pop-out hole, and protect whatever table or mat you are playing on.  Also included is a separate lid, similarly felt lined, and attached via strong rare-earth magnets to the template tray (which also has integral magnets).  The magnets are strong enough that you can hold the whole tray upside down with templates inside, without losing them.  Also, the magnets allow you to take the lid off during use and snap it in place underneath the main tray during use.
This has been an evolution of the very popular Highbridge template tray, and I'm very proud to offer this next iteration.  You're absolutely going to love this tray.  
As with all of my items, please feel free to contact me about customization.  Painted trays and custom laser engraving are popular add-ons.  Please note that I won't engrave copywrited logos for which I do not have the rights.  (No Star Wars logo or FFG X-Wing logo)
This tray is not a product of, or endorsed by, Fantasy Flight Games.  However, if you're not upgrading your cardboard tokens and templates when you get the chance, you're doing it wrong.  They're even specifically allowed in sanctioned X-wing tournament events.

Product name: Senet: board game from Ancient Egypt
Description:
The Senet, invented in ancient Egypt, is one of the oldest games known. This board game made ââof wood by hand is inspired by the Senet of Amenhotep III (fourteenth century BC) which is now on permanent display at the Brooklyn Museum in New York. A more modern reference to the game Senet is in the American show Lost where, in the sixth season, Jacob character plays a game with a Senet board located on the beach.
The game of Senet was very popular in all the social statements in Ancient Egypt. Several board games or references to Senet were found in royal tombs such as Tutankamon's tomb, Nefertari's or Amenothep's.
Some archaeologinst are also supporting the hypothesis that Egyptian people attributed to the Senet a magical or symbolic character and the game was a reference to the Book of the Dead, representing the Judgment of Osiris, the victory of the deceased and the entry into the Duat.
SIZE: 30 x 11 x 6 cm

Product name: Claddagh Ring Irish Celtic Black Zirconium Wedding Band 9mm Promise Anniversay Commitment Celtic Claddagh Comfort Fit Mens Womens Sizes 4-16
Description:
Black Zirconium Wedding Ring, Irish Claddagh Ring, Promise Ring, Couple Wedding Bands, Black Zirconium Claddagh Ring, Zirconium Wedding Bands, Black Rings, Zirconium Wedding Bands
Black Zirconium
Black Zirconium is a natural element found on earth. It is  bio-compatible, non-toxic.Black Zirconium is  naturally Silver colored metal and it  is typically used in dental implants and nuclear reactors. When Zirconium heated a black oxidized coating formed. The outer black jet color layer like a shell becomes very hard like a sapphire,which is harder than Titanium, but not as hard as Tungsten. This coating makes Zirconium Rings scratch resistant and allows us to create beautiful two toned styles. Black Zirconium offers the highest design versatility of any performance metal.
Black Zirconium Bands with  special engravings are non-refundable and exchangeable.
This ring is made by order one-at-a-time. It normally takes 14 to 20 business days to create Black Zirconium Wedding Band.
For Custom Made  Black Zirconium Rings available sizes are from size 3 up to size 20, the available width is from 2mm up to 20mm or 3/4 inches.
There is 20% price increase for any Zirconium Ring size above size 13.
Black Zirconium wedding Rings are extremely durable with normal daily wear, but take it off when you perform activities when you suppose to have the gloves on and you do not or when jewelry is forbidden to wear for a safety reason.
                                                The Meaning Of Claddagh Ring
The Claddagh ring ( Irish : Fainne Chladaigh) is a Traditional Irish Ring which represents love, loyalty and friendship. 
Hands represent Friendship, 
Heart represents Love,
Crown represent Loyalty.
This beautiful Titanium Claddagh Ring can be worn as a Friendship Ring, but are most commonly used as a Promise Ring, Engagement Ring and Wedding Band.
The ring is Comfort Fit which means that the shank on the inside is rounded for extra comfort.

Product name: On The Loom: A Weavers Guide
Description:
In On the Loom, Maryanne Moodie brings the ancient art of weaving to the modern day in a comprehensive guide packed with step-by-step tutorials and beautiful photography. Learn the basics of this simple and beautiful craft with valuable information on basic stitches, tools needed, and even how to make your own looms. Split by loom typeâcircular, rectangular, and even found objectsâ24 lush, bohemian, and uniquely modern projects for the home and to wear draw deeply on the nostalgic quality of vintage textiles. In addition to the how-to, this is the ultimate resource for finding your own creativity and style through this medium, from learning which materials to use for different effects to discovering how to use color to create vintage-inspired projects with a modern twist.
ABOUT THE AUTHOR
Maryanne Moodie is a professional textile artist and teacher. Her work has been featured in New York Magazine, Anthology, and O, the Oprah Magazine, and online on Design*Sponge and The Design Files. A finalist in the Martha Stewart American Made Awards in both 2014 and 2015, she sells her work on Etsy and through online shops and boutiques around the country.

Dried hops flowers(cones) make a beautiful and interesting botanical addition to any celebration. 
These hops flowers are hand selected, dried, wired with a 1.5 inch length of florist wire and wrapped with florist tape for convenient boutonniere construction.  Each wired hop is securely attached to a cardboard backer with a wire tie for shipping.  The flowers range in size from 1.0 inch to 1.5 inches. Just let us know the date you would like your shipment to arrive and we will ship accordingly.  For maximum color retention purposes, we advise that you have your hops arrive to you no earlier than 2 weeks prior to your wedding/event.
The hops flowers will arrive as pictured above, attached to cardboard backing and carefully wrapped and packaged.  (The third picture with the rye stalks is for demonstration purposes only.) Storage instructions for the hops will be enclosed with the order. 
This item includes step by step instructions with full color photos detailing how to make beautiful hops boutonnieres.  Tips for personalizing the boutonnieres are shown in the instructions.   
Extra Bonus:  Each order includes 2  extra wired stem hops to be used for practice purposes.

Product name: Organic Whole Milk - Live Milk Kefir Grains - Fast growing!
Description:
Live Organic Whole Milk Kefir grains ready to start making you Kefir at home!  Our grains are used daily in a non-refrigerated, organic, RAW milk environment and they are actively making Kefir - daily!  These grains ferment fast, and also grow fast.  We 100% guarantee that these grains will work very well!  After shipping, allow them a few batches, and then they will take off!  Whichever size you choose - we will ship you grains straight from one of our non-refrigerated organic raw milk active batches.  
*NOTE: Some customers have asked what type of milk these grains work best with.  These grains love whole milk!  We use them primarily in organic raw whole milk, but I have seen them successfully used in batches of store brand whole milk that is not ultra-pasteurized.  So it is your choice how you want to use them - just make sure you are using whole milk that is not ultra-pasteurized.  For daily consumption, start with 2-3 cups of milk, and then adjust accordingly based on your preference.
**SHIPPING:  Since this is a living, organic product, there may be some concerns regarding shipping and delivery time.  Our grains are extremely hardy and we have shipped them successfully across the country.  The default Shipping option is to send them out via USPS First-Class Mail.  This means that they will roughly take 1-3 days to get to your destination.  If the grains are ordered close to a weekend (Thursday, Friday, Saturday - then please account for an extra day of shipping due to no service on Sunday).  We pack our grains in containers with a bit of dried organic milk to eat on the trip, and then we put these containers into padded envelopes - so they will be fine when they get to you, but they will be hungry and need to get into milk immediately upon delivery.  If shipping duration is a concern and you need your grains faster, please send us a conversation message or select the Shipping Upgrade Option at Checkout to have them sent to you via USPS Priority Express, and we will send them via 1-day delivery service.
Select the size variation you want when checking out:  
1) We can ship you a tablespoon of live Kefir grains (straight from an active batch)
2) We can ship you a teaspoon of live Kefir grains (straight from an active batch)
One tablespoon is equal to 3 teaspoons!  We give you more than enough to get you started making Kefir right away!  Our Kefir grains are very active, and usually ferment within 8-10 hours.  They may be a little slow the first few batches you create due to the stress of shipping, but just keep them in milk and they will start cranking!  You will also notice that grains will start to grow and multiply after about 4-5 batches.  If you DO NOT want to take on a bunch of growing grains right away or want to only make a little bit of Kefir at a time, get the teaspoon size.  If they grow too fast for you, you can store them safely for up to 3 weeks in the refrigerator.  Remember - they are living!
Our Kefir grains are accustomed to Organic Raw Milk, and Organic Whole Milk, but they work great with non-organic whole milk as well.  They are used to operating in a temperature range of 68-72 degrees.  They do best in a ratio of 1 tablespoon to 2 cups of milk.  We also recommend a teaspoon to 1 cup of milk.  You can always play with the milk ratio to adjust the amount of separation you get.  They also work great for a second fermentation to get your Kefir a little extra kick.
There are 14.3 grams in one tablespoon.  We ship you Kefir grains in a 15 gram container.
There is slightly less than 4 grams in one teaspoon.  We ship you Kefir grains in a 5 gram container.

14K Gold Filled Jewelry 
Gold Fill is a thick layer of 14k solid gold, that has been bonded with another metal, usually copper or brass. When cared for correctly, due to the thick sold gold layer, 14k gold fill, unlike gold plating, will not tarnish or discolor. Your jewelry will last as long as, & will wear exactly like solid gold.

THE GREEK EVIL EYE CHARM
The evil eye or "mati" as it is known in Greece, has been holding a special place in Greek tradition since the ancient times. Product name: Wonder Woman Boots, bootlet shoe covers. Handmade original.
Description:
The Original "Bootlets"
These fit on over your own shoe to make any size shoe or heel into a boot. Made of lycra. The front sole is leather-look vinyl and there is a hole at the back to fit your own heel through. 
I invented this particular design in the 1980s when I was head designer for a clothing manufacturer. They were not meant to be for resale; only a fashion accessory for one of our photo shoots. To our surprise, when the catalog came out, we had a flood of inquiries from interested buyers about where they could buy the faux boots. Over the years I have improved upon them, taking suggestions and testing various styles and fabrics. I decided to make them in a variety of colors and styles for cosplay such as Wonder Woman, Supergirl, Batgirl, Catwoman, Sailor Moon, etc. I still make each pair myself by hand to this day. Many have tried to copy them since, but these are the original. 
One size fits most. They can be worn over most shoe sizes, heels or flats, and toe style (pointy, square, rounded). 
If you need a specific color to match your costume, please send us a message, and we can make something just for you. Color shades can vary, so piecing together your costume from several other sources is not recommended. 
MEASUREMENTS:
WOMENS SIZE:

CUSTOM MADE:
Please include your leg and foot measurements in the note when you order.
*It is not recommended these be worn over actual boots or running shoes. The fabric is smooth and very stretchy, so any zippers, laces, thick straps or buckles will look lumpy underneath the lycra material of the bootlet. A plain shoe is the best option. 
Plan on doing some serious walking or dancing? Add these non-skid sole protectors to your cart when ordering: 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/254356690/sole-protectors-for-bootlets
There can be no returns on bootlets once the sole protectors are adhered to the bootlets.
Care instructions: 
Hand wash, hang to dry. Do not wring or iron. May be dry-cleaned if preferred.
Quality:
Savilla Creations pieces are hand made with care in the USA, and one-of-a-kind. I use American and/or Canadian materials which are environmentally friendly and vegan.
All of our collection is created in a clean, smoke-free environment. Our security guard is a mighty 5-pound Chihuahua who sounds an alarm when anyone enters the premises, however he is not involved in the creative process in any way. I can ensure everything I make for you has been done so in a thoughtful manner; and I put love and kindness into each piece. Everything you receive is packaged carefully and mindfully. 
My effort is always to make your experience a special one and meet all your expectations of quality as well as value, so if you have questions regarding this or special requests please contact me.
